{"tid":2413791,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Volkswagen傳分拆旗下保時捷上市","createTime":"2021-02-19T03:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T06:09:34.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"afd0ff27b11c3b5d4aca3061618df18335983fdc","tid":2413791,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕德國福斯集團（Volkswagen Group）傳出正在考慮，要讓旗下豪華品牌Volkswagen（Porsche）獨立上市，以提高該品牌的估值，並藉此帶來大量現金。知情人士稱，儘管現在還沒有做出任何決定，但最快可能明年就會公開上市。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，知情人士透露，福斯集團正在與顧問討論，研究分拆保時捷或將其IPO的益處。知情人士還稱，福斯集團可以把保時捷IPO的收益，拿來收購或是投資技術。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3443092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3443092&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Kix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=6451b972\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3443092&h=f1f789f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3443092</a>"},{"pid":"a330744a33c289726a3c8b657f48040837bfa6be","tid":2413791,"uid":39750,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"原本係Porsche收購VW 不過VW同德國政府使橫手阻止 搞到Porsche margin call差啲破埋產 搞到VW有平貨汁"},{"pid":"7f2e24e4726d877aaa7f6a77e648427377cf50a2","tid":2413791,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a330744a33c289726a3c8b657f48040837bfa6be","tid":2413791,"uid":39750,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"原本係Porsche收購VW 不過VW同德國政府使橫手阻止 搞到Porsche margin call差啲破埋產 搞到VW有平貨汁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"Gme<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4945aa20ef9f6c61a7359579e3a2fce448e8084","tid":2413791,"uid":52221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a330744a33c289726a3c8b657f48040837bfa6be","tid":2413791,"uid":39750,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"r